- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for 3 patterns with `#if NET7_0_OR_GREATER` fallback — L12-33
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()` — L157-168
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `.ToLowerInvariant()` correctly — L189
